title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show NOV-07-2013 THURS
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show NOV-07-2013 THURS







Thursday, November 07, 2013


Mike On The Tea Party





 
 

 - 9AM hour

Guest: Steve Malanga, Manhattan Institute ..
      Discussion of NY Mayor-elect, Bill de Blasio





 - 10AM hour

Guest: Derrick Wilburn, founder, President and Chairman of the Board
        of the Rocky Mountain Black Conservatives,
         American Conservatives of Color,
           and BlackandConservative.com 

 "Bloomberg and the Invasion of Colorado."





 - 11AM hour

Mike discusses his column in today's Denver Post,

     "Tea Party must learn to embrace coalition politics."
